{"tid":487152,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"坤 哥 床 上 撩 女 開 Live  話 要 同 16 歲 學 生 妹 傳 緋 聞","createTime":"2017-12-02T13:21:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-03T00:24:22.000Z","uid":35964,"like":5,"dislike":243,"uniUserReply":58,"replies":[{"pid":"a0001055f706d2cefb720752667d4b67fa0f2e80","tid":487152,"uid":35964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T13:21:54.000Z","msg":"偽毒坤哥（吳業坤）向來都鍾意食好西，食埋食埋唔少好嘢就係人都知，昨晚佢喺IG開live，身在韓國酒店床上，着住粉藍色勁cute睡衣，敷住個面膜，再加埋佢個清裝頭髮型，瞓喺床度度撩人傾計，佢真識食一開始就同一個只有16歲嘅學生妹黄淑蔓傾，兩個人各自瞓喺床度，搞到個女仔有啲尷尬，原來佢哋係兩年前同一屆新人，坤哥攞金奬黄淑蔓就攞銅奬，睇返個女仔ig發現坤哥都有搵人jam歌合唱，唔通呢個女仔都係坤哥目標之一。<br />\n<br />\n除咗同黄淑蔓傾之外，坤哥仲同之前傳過緋聞嘅王卓琪一齊傾計，不過叫咗人哋開live，唔夠2秒唔夠就踢走人，好冇風度囉！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://vmagimg.next.hk/images/apple/20171201/large/1512121357_1dba.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvmagimg.next.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple%2F20171201%2Flarge%2F1512121357_1dba.jpg&h=fded8720&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b929b62be3c2941397eefa31788aad45999eccd3","tid":487152,"uid":95508,"like":284,"dislike":2,"score":282,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T13:58:19.000Z","msg":"條髮線去左邊"},{"pid":"7275a6b610d6c0a53a2c26b4402b6612d1569fa2","tid":487152,"uid":37005,"like":337,"dislike":3,"score":334,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T14:02:30.000Z","msg":"呢隻狗坤真係好撚噁心<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大大隻鹹濕兩隻字鑿喺額頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4211116598bd8159867f455e944be228ecd9f46d","tid":487152,"uid":24491,"like":14,"dislike":65,"score":-51,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T14:05:05.000Z","msg":"唔講以為係c君<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9db3a05c5b2cb05d7c43f6954f847f4809d8977","tid":487152,"uid":92459,"like":5,"dislike":6,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T14:05:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢隻狗坤真係好撚噁心<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大大隻鹹濕兩隻字鑿喺額頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"